ts-listening/ielts-cambridge-5-test-4-part-1-2023-08-09-22-33-54/49.mp3","time_start":157.87,"time_end":163.08},{"position":50,"content":"somewhere I could sit and be peaceful.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-5-test-4-part-1-2023-08-09-22-33-54/50.mp3","time_start":163.35,"time_end":165.92},{"position":51,"content":"Is that all?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-5-test-4-part-1-2023-08-09-22-33-54/51.mp3","time_start":165.92,"time_end":167.07},{"position":52,"content":"Well... I'm really serious about improving my English","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-5-test-4-part-1-2023-08-09-22-33-54/52.mp3","time_start":167.63,"time_end":172.56},{"position":53,"content":"so I'd prefer to be the only guest if that's possible?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-5-test-4-part-1-2023-08-09-22-33-54/53.mp3","time_start":172.56,"time_end":177.17},{"position":54,"content":"No other guests...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-5-test-4-part-1-2023-08-09-22-33-54/54.mp3","time_start":177.17,"time_end":178.89},{"position":55,"content":"Yes, you get more practice that way.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-5-test-4-part-1-2023-08-09-22-33-54/55.mp3","time_start":178.89,"time_end":181.02},{"position":56,"content":"Anyway, obviously all this is partly dependent on how much you're willing to pay.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-5-test-4-part-1-2023-08-09-22-33-54/56.mp3","time_start":181.28,"time_end":186.4},{"position":57,"content":"What did you have in mind?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-5-test-4-part-1-2023-08-09-22-33-54/57.mp3","time_start":186.56,"time_end":188.17},{"position":58,"content":"I was thinking in terms o